08:11.064 --> 08:13.599
<i>- (Faint whirring)
- Woman: Who are you?</i>

08:13.600 --> 08:17.402
Uh, Ned Weeks. I spoke to
you after the "Times" article.

08:19.072 --> 08:20.305
Come in. Take your clothes off.

08:20.306 --> 08:22.607
