08:26.145 --> 08:27.812
You are gay, aren't you?

08:27.813 --> 08:29.848
Yes.

08:29.849 --> 08:31.483
Take your clothes off. Don't be nervous.

08:31.484 --> 08:34.284
I've seen more men than you have.

08:37.857 --> 08:40.424
<i>Doctor: To answer all of
your questions, I don't know.</i>

08:40.424 --> 08:44.028
<i>I've never seen or heard
of anything like this.</i>

08:44.029 --> 08:45.730
Have you had any of the symptoms?

08:45.731 --> 08:47.898
Most of the shit the "Times" said...

08:47.899 --> 08:50.001
amoebas, gonorrhea, hepatitis.

08:50.002 --> 08:52.603
