system we know the least about.

09:28.539 --> 09:30.806
So where's this big
mouth I hear you've got?

09:30.807 --> 09:33.076
- Is big mouth a symptom?
- No.

09:33.077 --> 09:34.911
It's a cure.

09:34.912 --> 09:37.146
This seems to only be happening to gay men.

09:37.147 --> 09:40.349
Buzzy says you are well-known
in the gay community

09:40.350 --> 09:42.752
<i>and not afraid to say what you think.</i>

09:42.753 --> 09:45.087
I can't find any gay leaders

09:45.088 --> 09:48.824
and I call gay organizations,
no one ever calls me back.

09:48.825 --> 09:52.428
Dr. Brookner, no one with half a
brain gets involved with gay politics.

09:52.429 --> 09:54.763
- There's no room for criticism.
- What's your criticism?

09:54.764 --> 09:56.231
I hate that we play victim

09:56.232 --> 09:57.999
when many of us, most of us, don't have to.

09:58.000 --> 09:59.834
Then you're exactly what's needed now.

09:59.835 --> 10:01.937
Maybe they're just waiting
for someone to lead them.

10:01.938 --> 10:03.539
