10:03.540 --> 10:06.108
What exactly are you
trying to get me to do?

10:06.109 --> 10:08.243
Tell gay men to stop having sex.

10:10.345 --> 10:13.014
Do you think that this cancer
is sexually transmitted?

10:13.015 --> 10:14.816
I think it is, yes.

10:14.817 --> 10:17.251
Can I prity it yet? No.

10:19.354 --> 10:21.623
Do you realize that you're talking about

10:21.624 --> 10:23.291
millions of men

10:23.292 --> 10:25.226
who have singled out promiscuity

10:25.227 --> 10:27.495
as their principal political agenda?

10:27.496 --> 10:30.798
<i>- How do you deal with that?
- Tell them they may die.</i>

10:30.799 --> 10:34.102
- Where?
- Down the hall. Down the hall!

10:34.103 --> 10:37.037
It's not that simple. It's
more complicated than that.

10:37.038 --> 10:38.839
