You can go. I'm not finding
what I'm looking for here.

10:49.985 --> 10:51.485
<i>(Elevator bell rings)</i>

10:51.486 --> 10:54.287
<i>- Bruce: Where?
- Mickey: Open up!</i>

10:54.288 --> 10:56.223
- Where? Where?
- Right in that room.

10:56.224 --> 10:59.126
Just put him up on the table.

10:59.127 --> 11:01.161
Up here. Let's find a pulse.

11:01.162 --> 11:03.163
Baby, easy.

11:03.164 --> 11:05.698
- Be still.
- Buzzy: Can you tell me what happened?

11:05.699 --> 11:07.900
We were meeting him outside.

11:07.901 --> 11:09.802
We turned the corner and he just collapsed.

11:09.803 --> 11:12.639
<i>- (Horns honking)
- (Panting)</i>

11:12.640 --> 11:15.308
(Tires screech)

11:15.309 --> 11:16.809
Jesus!

11:16.810 --> 11:19.178
Hey, get the fuck out of the street!

11:20.648 --> 11:23.149
- (Gasping)
- Baby!

11:23.150 --> 11:25.685
- Oh, my God!
- Help!

11:25.686 --> 11:28.320
<i>- (Sobbing)
- (Siren blaring)</i>

11:30.124 --> 11:31.724
- Who's the lover?
- I am, ma'am.

11:31.725 --> 11:33.959
- What's your name?
- Bruce Niles.

11:33.960 --> 11:36.395
Brookner. I need a room immediately.

11:36.396 --> 11:38.531
Niles, you were Reinhardt's boyfriend.

11:38.532 --> 11:39.998
