12:42.760 --> 12:45.429
It can happen this fast?

12:46.431 --> 12:48.665
It just did.

12:57.742 --> 13:00.944
We have to do something.

13:00.945 --> 13:03.279
No one else will.

13:03.280 --> 13:05.982
<i>Mickey: What are we supposed to do?</i>

13:10.420 --> 13:13.623
<i>Morton: You make these assumptions
on the basis of 46 cases.</i>

13:13.624 --> 13:17.159
You wanted to know what I
think. This is what I think.

13:17.160 --> 13:19.295
You are all going to infect each other.

13:19.296 --> 13:21.464
(Clamoring)

13:24.968 --> 13:27.603
