13:36.780 --> 13:38.580
<i>and how they got around.</i>

13:38.581 --> 13:40.482
Where are the medical
journals? The "Times"?

13:40.483 --> 13:43.752
I sent my first reports to the
medical journals over a year ago.

13:43.753 --> 13:46.388
Excuse me, how do you know
what you're looking for,

13:46.389 --> 13:49.157
real quick, if you don't
know what you're looking for?

13:49.158 --> 13:50.958
<i>I'm sorry, I guess that's a dumb question.</i>

13:50.959 --> 13:53.561
No, it isn't. It's the
smartest question of all

13:53.562 --> 13:55.363
and the hardest one to answer.

13:55.364 --> 13:58.065
Doesn't common sense tell you
you should cool it for a while?

13:58.066 --> 14:00.134
