be that you cooled it for a while.

14:12.147 --> 14:14.615
- (Clamoring)
- No, excuse me. Excuse me.

14:14.616 --> 14:17.785
Excuse me. That is not the
worst that will have happened.

14:17.786 --> 14:19.920
