15:17.043 --> 15:19.278
<i>Man: Next time, bring some fucking food.</i>

15:19.279 --> 15:21.413
<i>Tommy: Hey, hey, hey. That's not nice.</i>

15:25.718 --> 15:28.119
Welcome to gay politics.

15:59.384 --> 16:02.453
Yeah, I'm very late for an important
meeting with Craig Claiborne.

16:02.454 --> 16:04.555
