16:07.058 --> 16:09.427
(Phones ringing, typewriter keys clicking)

16:20.104 --> 16:22.339
- Hi, Felix Turner.
- And you are?

16:22.340 --> 16:25.108
My name's Ned Weeks.

16:25.109 --> 16:27.177
You're very cute.

16:27.178 --> 16:30.279
You caught me at a rough moment, all right?

16:30.280 --> 16:32.214
I have a deadline. The
First Lady is coming to town.

16:32.215 --> 16:34.818
I've been told you're
gay and you might be able

16:34.819 --> 16:37.053
