37:31.435 --> 37:34.371
No?

37:34.372 --> 37:37.207
It's because you're too good to be true,

37:37.208 --> 37:39.676
because I've been waiting for
a lover like you my whole life,

37:39.677 --> 37:41.311
you haven't showed up until now,

37:41.312 --> 37:44.514
and I'm scared shitless that I'm
